  "about_the_game": "Classic color match <strong>puzzle</strong> meets space <strong>shoot'em up</strong> action! Hop into your spaceship, open a path through huge waves of aliens and other hazards, and face intense boss battles!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three difficulty modes.<br></li><li>Randomized color puzzle stages.<br></li><li>Intense shoot'em up boss fights.<br></li><li>Unlock, buy and upgrade new ships.<br></li><li>Unlockable Boss Rush mode.<br></li><li>Colorful and polished pixel art graphics.<br></li><li>Arcade-like FM synth soundtrack.</li></ul>",
